THE ART OF NEW YORK is an extraordinary homage to the vitality, power, beauty and magic of a great city For the first time, paintings, drawings, sculptures, and prints by leading twentieth-century artists have been gathered together to form an insightful, loving portrait of "Oz on the Hudson."
